99	    // ── Admin-only ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
100	
101	    // ── Foundational entity writes (admin-only, no /admin prefix) ───
102	    // These mutate billing- and operations-critical baselines and must
103	    // never be available to staff or group-leaders, per requirements.
104	    //
105	    // Each route also carries a `permission:*` slug. The role:admin
106	    // gate is the hard role boundary; the permission slug is the
107	    // feature-level identifier the UI introspects so individual
108	    // buttons can be conditionally rendered (see GET /auth/me's
