244	    /**
245	     * Apply the same role-aware row-level scoping as listSettlementsForUser
246	     * but to a custom date-bounded query, returning a Collection (not a
247	     * paginator). Used by the export pipeline so CSV/PDF outputs always
248	     * match what the user sees on screen.
249	     */
